snippet.title: Vertical Asymptote Vs. Removable Discontinuity
snippet.description:
In this video, I show an example on how to find the Horizontal asymptote, vertical asymptote and removable discontinuity from a rational function. 
Horizontal Asymptote, @0:10
Vertical Asymptote @4:16
Removable Discontinuity @6:47
